  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The calls should extract method name then resolve an RpcRequestHandler\r\n\r\nRpcRequestHandler should be an abstract class from which a specific, e.g. EthBlockNumber should inherit.\r\n(we have done similar code for Catalyst and it avoid a lot of nonsense there)\r\n\r\nThen we should invoke the method with parameters and with the response body stream passed directly.\r\n\r\nEach handler should support 'smart' cached responses. For example on eth_getBlockByNumber or eth_blockNumber we can easily cache the most likely responses already serialized.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/498913/73614530-3fa5db80-4600-11ea-8cbc-3cb053ceef90.png)\r\n\r\n",
